{Speech 64 Answer 67}{}{Done. They agree to help us. Here's the emergency radio code. You'll discuss the details in person with Sheiman.}
{Speech 64 Answer 65}{}{Done. They agree to help us. Here's the emergency radio code. And on top of that, he agrees to take our soldiers on for training.}
{Speech 64 Answer 66}{}{Done. They agree to help us. Here's the emergency radio code. And on top of that, he agrees to take our soldiers on for training.}
{Speech 65}{}{Excellent, @pname@! I believed in you, but I didn't expect a result like this. Well, I'll reward you. From me personally - a personalized weapon, and a cash bonus, of course.}
{Speech 65 Answer 68}{}{Serving the people!}
{Speech 66}{}{Excellent, @pname@! I believed in you, but I didn't expect a result like this. Well, I'll reward you. From this moment you are a @sex@|Citizen|Citizen| of Vault City. From me personally - a personalized weapon, and a cash bonus, of course.}
{Speech 66 Answer 68}{}{Serving the people!}
{Speech 67}{}{Not bad, very good, @pname@! You greatly @sex@|helped|helped| the whole City. And the city is grateful to you. Take this.}
{Speech 67 Answer 68}{}{Serving the people!}
{Speech 68}{}{And you serve well! By the way, allow me to congratulate you. You're a lieutenant now. Your pay is 360 coins a day. Any treatment from Doctor Troy is free. Three super stimpaks a week from him too. Valerie will repair three of any items a day…\nI think we ought to wet those bars.}
